data.description: INCREDIBLE OPPORTUNITY!  Perfectly appointed and carefully crafted, this custom Colonial w/ resort-style backyard is found sprawled over a full acre of professionally manicured grounds on a secluded cul-de-sac street! Wrapped in cedar shakes and showcasing an outdoor oasis that has been renovated to perfection, the interior of this home is equally remarkable and loaded with artful updates.  Stainless steel appliances equip a gourmet eat-in kitchen with center island, while custom millwork, exposed beams and built-ins accent the family and living rooms. This custom floor plan features 5 bedrooms with an optional 6th, 4 full bathrooms, 2 half bathrooms, and a first floor guest suite with full bathroom and its own private entrance. The upper level master suite hosts a dream-like ensuite bath with double vanity and oversized jacuzzi tub. A finished full basement offers a private office, wet bar, lounge area, bathroom and walk-out to one of 2 garages, which offer the capacity to hold 3 total cars. The MASSIVE backyard is designed with entertainment and functionality in mind, featuring an in-ground pool with waterfall, huge paver patio with fire pit, covered patio, storage shed, and ample lawn space on level grounds. An absolute must see that will not last long!
